kamoto\\\">\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n            <h2>\\u00bfQui\\u00e9n es Satoshi Nakamoto?<\\/h2>\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n                Satoshi Nakamoto es el pseud\\u00f3nimo del creador de Bitcoin, la primera criptomoneda. Desde su aparici\\u00f3n en 2008 con el whitepaper hasta el lanzamiento de la red en 2009, su identidad ha permanecido oculta. Nadie sabe qui\\u00e9n est\\u00e1 detr\\u00e1s de este nombre, lo que genera un gran misterio.\\r\\n            <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Section 2 -->\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n            <h2>El Enigma del Creador<\\/h2>\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n                Existen varias teor\\u00edas sobre qui\\u00e9n podr\\u00eda ser Nakamoto. Algunos sospechan que es una sola persona, mientras que otros creen que es un grupo. Entre los posibles candidatos se encuentran Hal Finney, Nick Szabo y Craig Wright, pero hasta ahora ninguno ha demostrado ser el verdadero creador.\\r\\n            <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n            <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/bitcoin.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Bitcoin\\\">\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Section 3 -->\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n            <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/blockchain.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Blockchain\\\">\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n            <h2>\\u00bfPor qu\\u00e9 es importante el misterio?<\\/h2>\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n                El misterio de Satoshi ha dado forma a la filosof\\u00eda de las criptomonedas. Su anonimato refuerza la idea de descentralizaci\\u00f3n. Al no haber un l\\u00edder claro, Bitcoin ha demostrado que puede operar sin una autoridad central, algo \\u00fanico en el mundo financiero.\\r\\n            <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/body>\\r\\n<\\/html>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":8,\"created\":\"2025-01-01 14:37:39\",\"created_by\":\"209\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2025-01-05 12:19:03\",\"modified_by\":208,\"checked_out\":208,\"checked_out_time\":\"2025-01-05 12:18:56\",\"publish_up\":\"2025-01-01 14:38:14\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ulti